	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Feb 11th 12:59 PM 2002</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent<span id=notbold>[3.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am an Erudite Paladin (&quot;The Proud, The Few&quot;), and am currently wearing a Cold Iron Breastplate (AC: 17 Magic Resist: +3)<br><br>I'm thinking of switching to the Midnight Sea Mail Coat (AC:15 Str:+3 Wis:+3 Cold Resist:+10)<br><br>My question is, would you guys rather have the extra AC of the CIB, or the stat bonuses of the MSMC?<br><br>As an Erudite I can always use the extra Str, plus the MSMC only weighs 5.1 whereas the CIB weighs 12.5.&nbsp;&nbsp;I leaning toward the MSMC.  Opinions?<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Mon Feb 11 13:00:18 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
