	   <tr><td colspan=2>I'm also a fan of begging while attacking mobs to help hold aggro on top of everything said above.&nbsp;&nbsp;You'll have to switch off attack to do it, but it's easy to mix begging in with your taunt, FoL, stun combo. I'm not sure how much extra hate this generates, but it seems to help.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
