	   <tr><td colspan=2>Greetings Ratzmandious and welcome to Norrath!<br><br>You will receive the ability to use spells at level 9.&nbsp;&nbsp;I would suggest that you purchase all the spells available...with the exception perhaps of True North!  If you work on your Sense Heading skill...which you should do regularly...True North has little use.  All the other spells have their particular uses. Some more than others, obviously, but plan on buying them all.<br><br>Good luck!<br><br>Kneesmasher Ayebulger<br>Dwarven Knight<br>Torvonnilous Server<br><br>&quot;Never Mistake Kindness for Weakness&quot;<br>&nbsp;<br>Kneesmasher Ayebulger<br>Dwarven Knight<br>Torvonnilous Server<br><br>"Never Mistake Kindness for Weakness"</td></tr>
